<article id="post-765875" class="post-765875 digital-library type-digital-library status-publish has-post-thumbnail hentry category-architecture-and-hardware category-data-and-information section-research-highlights">

			
<header class="article-header article-header--default">
	<div class="article-header__inner container">
		<div class="article-header__section"><a href="https://cacm.acm.org/section/research-highlights/">Research Highlights</a></div>
		<div class="article-header__topic-and-issue-section">
			<span class="article-header__topic">
			<a href="https://cacm.acm.org/category/architecture-and-hardware/">Architecture and Hardware</a>			</span>
			<span class="article-header__issue-section">
							</span>
		</div>
		<h1 class="article-header__title">Many Faces of Ad Hoc Transactions</h1>
					<div class="article-header__subtitle"><p>Interesting, perceptive, and potentially alarming findings from a comprehensive study of real-world ad hoc transactions.</p>
</div>
		
		<div class="article-header__meta">
			<div class="article-header__byline">
				By <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/chuzhe-tang/" title="Posts by Chuzhe Tang" class="author url fn" rel="author">Chuzhe Tang</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/zhaoguo-wang/" title="Posts by Zhaoguo Wang" class="author url fn" rel="author">Zhaoguo Wang</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/xiaodong-zhang/" title="Posts by Xiaodong Zhang" class="author url fn" rel="author">Xiaodong Zhang</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/qianmian-yu/" title="Posts by Qianmian Yu" class="author url fn" rel="author">Qianmian Yu</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/binyu-zang/" title="Posts by Binyu Zang" class="author url fn" rel="author">Binyu Zang</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/haibing-guan/" title="Posts by Haibing Guan" class="author url fn" rel="author">Haibing Guan</a>, and <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/haibo-chen/" title="Posts by Haibo Chen" class="author url fn" rel="author">Haibo Chen</a>			</div>
			<div class="article-header__posted-on">
				<span class="posted-on">Posted <time datetime="2025-03-18T12:57:28-04:00">Mar 18 2025</time></span>			</div>
		</div>

			<figure class="article-header__figure article-header__figure--has-credit">
			<div class="image-wrapper image-wrapper--widescreen"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/030725.RH-Many-Faces-of-S.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="connected floating cubs, illustration" loading="eager" decoding="async" srcset="https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/030725.RH-Many-Faces-of-S.jpg 2400w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/030725.RH-Many-Faces-of-S.jpg?resize=300,169 300w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/030725.RH-Many-Faces-of-S.jpg?resize=768,432 768w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/030725.RH-Many-Faces-of-S.jpg?resize=1024,576 1024w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/030725.RH-Many-Faces-of-S.jpg?resize=1536,864 1536w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/030725.RH-Many-Faces-of-S.jpg?resize=2048,1152 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></div>			<figcaption><p class="article-header--credit">Credit: Yurchanka Siarhei / Shutterstock</p></figcaption>
